de_kismayo
by Oreo and Balefire
JazzBassKing@Hotmail.com
commissioned by usbongteam, uberkind@hotmail.com


Terrorists:  Infiltrate this city block in Kismayo, Somalia and 
destroy one of the two historical buildings near the river.

Counter-Terrorists:  Prevent the terrorists from destroying
the historical buildings.

Note:  This map was converted to de format from cs.  Please
try the cs version as well since the layout was originally
designed for hostage rescue.
